title: Secret Doctrine (CODEX)
description:
C O D E X
P R E S E N T S

Secret Doctrine (c) Elena Schukina

Release Date :  06/2017              Protection : Steam
Discs        :  1                    Genre      : Adventure

Secret Doctrine - 3d First Person Adventure, Puzzle.  Headline:  Do
we  always  know for  sure where  a subway  car is  taking  us  to?
Wherever it is traveling  to, it  is us  who choose  the  route.  A
routine trip back home turns into a course  of  unusual  adventures
for  the  hero  of  the story.  English -  full  audio,  subtitles;
Russian - full audio, subtitles; Chinese - subtitles.

For more info go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/645810/


MINIMUM:
OS: Windows 7 (32 bit)
Processor: Intel Core i3 or AMD equivalent
Memory: 4 GB RAM
Graphics: GeForce GTX950 or Radeon R7 370
DirectX: Version 11
Storage: 12 GB available space

RECOMMENDED:

Graphics:  GeForce GTX 1060 or Radeon RX 470
